sing the logarithmic Sobolev inequalities of the\nBr\\'ezis-Gallouet-Wainger and Beale-Kato-Majda types, respectively.\nSpecifically, a logarithmic Sobolev inequality of the limiting type, introduced\nin our previous work [12], is used, and a new logarithmic type Gronwall\ninequality is exploited.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Mar 2017 18:29:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-08"}
