role of\nthe total angular momenta of the interacting particles and of the complex,\nirrespective of their electronic or nuclear, orbital or spin nature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Mar 2017 13:46:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Apr 2017 13:58:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-11"}
