ions from oscillating to ballistic propagation of\nvortices, their interaction with pinning centers and standing nonlinear waves\nin the junction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Mar 2017 14:18:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-21"}
