ition of the atomic transition frequency with the gap of\nthe photonic crystal in the former case, and with the cut-off frequency of\nwaveguide in the latter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Mar 2017 15:32:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Aug 2017 08:07:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-24"}
